Antagony smiled and looked at the doggie as it ran up to her and Perndabot. 
She watched Vlad take it away and sighed. Cruelty to animals wasn't a good 
thing to watch, but some people still did it.

"That's ok," she replied to Vlad. She wanted to know more about this place, 
though, so she guessed that finding out this robot's name would be a good 
idea. "What's your name?" Antagony asked curiously in a polite tone. She 
wondered if this bot was friendly or not.
